ion, $f_{a}$, and so the form of the scalar potential, is completely\nfixed for a given value of $\\lambda_{\\phi}$, with only a weak dependence on\n$\\lambda_{\\phi}$. This will allow the inflation and post-inflation evolution of\nthe model to be quantitatively studied for a given inflation model and\ndimensionally natural values of $\\lambda_{\\phi}$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 2 Jul 2018 16:42:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 19 Jul 2018 13:20:49 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 14 Jan 2019 19:52:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-01-16"}
