doped SrIr$_2$O$_4$. We make testable theoretical predictions on\ncuprates and iridates. Finally, we note that there exist an unusually large\nnumber of unconventional superconductors that exhibit superconductivity\nproximate to exotic charge ordered states, whose bandfillings are also\n$\\frac{1}{4}$, exactly where the paired Wigner crystal is most stable.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 2 Jul 2018 19:57:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-12-05"}
