s\ncultural opinions of Wikipedia language editions. The world countries with the\nlargest number of top painters of selected 7 Wikipedia editions are found to be\nItaly, France, Russia. We argue that this approach gives meaningful information\nabout art and that it could be a part of extensive network analysis on human\nknowledge and cultures.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 3 Jul 2018 15:55:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-26"}
